    <TranslatableString name="CNEC_LESSON_STEP" id="9c428cce-7881-425e-bd98-97f6c1c11d2c">
        <constantUsages>
            <GlobalConstant name="CrLf"/>
        </constantUsages>
        <source>CNEC_LESSON_STEP = 
"The left hand panel displays a list of existing lessons. To work with an exisiting Lesson, select from the listbox - the Lesson details will then be displayed.
 To create a new Lesson, select the 'New' button." &amp; CrLf &amp; CrLf &amp;
"A Lesson contains a Header item plus multiple Activity items. The Activity items define the steps for the Lesson." &amp; CrLf &amp;  
"Create a new Activity by the 'New' button, or select an existing Activity from the listbox." &amp; CrLf &amp; CrLf &amp;
"As you modify Lesson and Activity text, the preview window shows how the lesson will look to the user. You may type directly into the Preview window."</source>
    </TranslatableString>
